How to Clear a Mechanical Pencil Lead Jam

We show you how to fix a jammed mechanical pencil by clearing out bits of broken lead. Follow along with pictures and step-by-step instructions to get your pencil writing again!

The Beginner's Guide to Fountain Pens

If you’ve never tried a fountain pen before, we really think you should give one a shot. We share some instructions and advice to help you get started, like how to install the ink and hold the pen. Happy writing!

How to Refill Lead for Multi Pens

Multi pens with mechanical pencil components are amazing useful, but it's not always easy to figure out how to refill the lead. Read our guide to see how to refill lead in your multi pen.
